<h2>Verify Your Email Address</h2>

<p>Hello {{firstName}},</p>

<p>Thank you for creating an account with Immobilier.ch! To complete your registration and access all features, please verify your email address.</p>

<div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
